DESCRIPTION:John Keats rightly said\, “A thing of beauty is a joy for ever.” The beauty of the natural world endures and inspires us through its quiet resilience. \n\nDiscover the beauty in nature's details through this nature journaling workshop led by Shilpashree\, a Bengaluru-based visual artist.
DTEND:20260307T090000Z
DTSTART:20260307T060000Z
SUMMARY:Decoding Nature Through Journaling
UID:1198@map-india.org
URL:https://map-india.org/map-events/decoding-nature-through-journaling/
