DTSTAMP:20260224T093034Z
DESCRIPTION:Whether you're a beginner\, a seasoned artist\, or simply curious\, this sketching session led by Penciljam invites you to explore and draw from a living garden.\n\nMAP's sculpture courtyard transforms into a garden with Living Botanicals — a space where plants native to the subcontinent grow\, change\, and are cared for over time.
DTEND:20260228T103000Z
